North Decimal Degree 43.3229 South Decimal Degree 42.9631 East Decimal Degree -1.2156 West Decimal Degree -2.0039 Relief shown by hachures. Principal meridian: Paris. Longitude is given in centesimal values (100 grades = 90 degrees) .The Service de la carte geologique de la France was integrated to the BRGM to become the only France Service geologique national.
